$ PowerShell: the preference variable $informationPreference
@ $informationPreference

The value of the → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/preference `$informationPreference` controls the behavior of → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/information/write[`write-information`]
-
Its value can be set to any member of the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Management/Automation/ActionPreference[`System.Management.Automation.ActionPreference` enum].

sa:

  The → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/host/write[PowerShell command verb `Write`]

  → Windows/PowerShell/command-inventory/noun/information/write[`write-information`]
